39d" class="promo-img" title="Koronavírus a Slovensko" alt="" data-reactid="317"/></a></article></div></div></div><!-- react-empty: 318 --></header></div><div data-reactid="319"><!-- react-empty: 320 --><nav class="container submenu" data-reactid="321"><ul class="submenu-menu menu menu--tabs list-reset clearfix" data-reactid="322"><li class="" data-reactid="323"><a href="http://www.tablet.tv/" rel="noopener" target="_blank" data-reactid="324">TABLET.TV</a></li><li class="" data-reactid="325"><a href="https://www.teraz.sk/tag/leto2020" rel="noopener" target="_blank" data-reactid="326">Leto na Slovensku</a></li></ul></nav><main data-reactid="327"><article class="article" data-reactid="328"><header class="articleHeader" data-reactid="329"><div class="container" data-reactid="330"><span class="container" data-reactid="331"><a href="/slovensko" data-reactid="332"><!-- react-text: 333 -->&lt; sekcia <!-- /react-text --><!-- react-text: 334 -->Slovensko<!-- /react-text --></a></span><h1 class="articleTitle" data-reactid="335">Prezidentka podpísala možnosť odkladu platby poistných odvodov</h1><div class="articleActions" data-reactid="336"><div class="articleActions-block" data-reactid="337"><iframe src="https://www.facebook.com/plugins/share_button.php?href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.teraz.sk%2Fslovensko%2Fprezidentka-podpisala-moznost-odkladu%2F458364-clanok.html&amp;layout=button_count&amp;size=large&amp;mobile_iframe=false&amp;appId=282867128448169&amp;width=110&amp;height=32" width="110" height="32" style="border:none;overflow:hidden;" scrolling="no" frameborder="0" allowtransparency="true" data-reactid="338"></iframe><a class="socialWidget socialWidget--twitter" href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.teraz.sk%2Fslovensko%2Fprezidentka-podpisala-moznost-odkladu%2F458364-clanok.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-reactid="339"><span class="socialWidget-label" data-reactid="340"><svg class="icon" data-reactid="341"><use xlink:href="/sprite.svg#twitter" data-reactid="342"></use></svg></span></a><a class="socialWidget socialWidget--comments" href="#diskusia" data-reactid="343"><span class="socialWidget-label" data-reactid="344"><svg class="icon" data-reactid="345"><use xlink:href="/sprite.svg#comments" data-reactid="346"></use></svg></span><span class="socialWidget-value" data-reactid="347"><div data-reactid="348"><span class="fb-comments-count" data-href="https://www.teraz.sk/slovensko/prezidentka-podpisala-moznost-odkladu/458364-clanok.html" data-reactid="349">.</span></div></span></a></div></div></div></header><div class="container" data-reactid="350"><div class="l-columns l-columns--article clearfix" data-reactid="351"><div class="articleContent l-main pull-left" data-reactid="352"><div class="articleImage aspectRatio" data-reactid="353"><img src="https://www3.teraz.sk/usercontent/photos/b/d/4/4-bd452520a2ad5790971f4f73d697eb0aaea6e545.jpg" title="Prezidentka podpísala možnosť odkladu platby poistných odvodov" alt="" data-reactid="354"/><div class="articleImageTop-caption" data-reactid="355"><figcaption data-reactid="356"><span>Na snímke prezidentka SR Zuzana Čaputov.</span> <em>Foto: TASR -  Michal Svítok</em><div class="clear"></div></figcaption></div></div><p class="articlePerex" data-reactid="357">Právnu normu parlament schválil v piatok (3.4.). Rokoval o nej v skrátenom legislatívnom konaní.</p><div class="articleMeta" data-reactid="358"><div class="clearfix" data-reactid="359"><span class="articleMeta-person" data-reactid="360"><!-- react-text: 361 -->Autor<!-- /react-text --><!-- react-text: 362 --> <!-- /react-text --><strong data-reactid="363"><a href="/author/11" data-reactid="364">TASR</a></strong></span></div><span class="publishingTime" data-reactid="365"><time datetime="2020-04-06T11:12:00+02:00" data-reactid="366">6. apríla 2020 11:12</time><!-- react-text: 367 -->,<!-- /react-text --><svg class="icon" data-reactid="368"><use xlink:href="/sprite.svg#repeat" data-reactid="369"></use></svg><span class="visuallyhidden" data-reactid="370">aktualizované</span><span data-reactid="371"> </span><time datetime="2020-04-06T11:19:00+02:00" data-reactid="372">6. apríla 2020 11:19</time></span></div><div data-reactid="373"><div id="9273640f-9acb-4488-9760-43c0b746ec49" class="articleMain" data-reactid="374"><div>Bratislava 6. apr&iacute;la (TASR) - &#268;as&#357; zamestn&aacute;vate&#318;ov a samostatne z&aacute;robkovo &#269;inn&yacute;ch os&ocirc;b (SZ&#268;O) bude m&ocirc;c&#357; vyu&#382;i&#357; odklad platenia poistn&eacute;ho na soci&aacute;lne poistenie, povinn&yacute;ch pr&iacute;spevkov na starobn&eacute; d&ocirc;chodkov&eacute; sporenie a preddavkov na zdravotn&eacute; poistenie za marec tohto roka. Uhradi&#357; po novom ich bud&uacute; m&ocirc;c&#357; a&#382; do 31. j&uacute;la tohto roka. Po&#269;&iacute;ta s t&yacute;m novela z&aacute;kona o soci&aacute;lnom poisten&iacute;, ktor&uacute; podp&iacute;sala prezidentka SR Zuzana &#268;aputov&aacute;.<br>
<br>
Pr&aacute;vnu normu parlament schv&aacute;lil v piatok (3.4.). Rokoval o nej v skr&aacute;tenom legislat&iacute;vnom konan&iacute;.<br>
<br>
Novelu na rokovanie predlo&#382;ilo ministerstvo pr&aacute;ce v reakcii na situ&aacute;ciu okolo nov&eacute;ho koronav&iacute;rusu. V oblasti soci&aacute;lneho poistenia a zdravotn&eacute;ho poistenia zav&aacute;dza mo&#382;nos&#357; odkladu povinnosti pre &#269;as&#357; zamestn&aacute;vate&#318;ov a SZ&#268;O zaplati&#357; poistn&eacute; na soci&aacute;lne poistenie, povinn&eacute; pr&iacute;spevky na starobn&eacute; d&ocirc;chodkov&eacute; sporenie a preddavky na zdravotn&eacute; poistenie, pri zamestn&aacute;vate&#318;och iba poistn&eacute; a preddavky na strane zamestn&aacute;vate&#318;a, za marec. Po novom ich bude mo&#382;n&eacute; zaplati&#357; v term&iacute;ne do 31. j&uacute;la 2020. Vl&aacute;da bude m&ocirc;c&#357; z&aacute;rove&#328; nariaden&iacute;m ustanovi&#357; &#271;al&scaron;&iacute; odklad povinnosti platenia poistn&eacute;ho.<br>
<br>
T&aacute;to mo&#382;nos&#357; sa bude t&yacute;ka&#357; zamestn&aacute;vate&#318;ov a povinne poisten&yacute;ch SZ&#268;O, ktor&iacute; vykazuj&uacute; pokles &#269;ist&eacute;ho obratu alebo pr&iacute;jmov z podnikania a z inej samostatnej z&aacute;robkovej &#269;innosti o 40 % a viac. Sp&ocirc;sob ur&#269;enia poklesu &#269;ist&eacute;ho obratu a pr&iacute;jmov z podnikania a z inej samostatnej z&aacute;robkovej &#269;innosti pod&#318;a osobitn&eacute;ho predpisu ustanov&iacute; vl&aacute;da nariaden&iacute;m.<br>
<br>
Poistn&eacute;, ktor&eacute; plat&iacute; zamestnanec a odv&aacute;dza ho jeho zamestn&aacute;vate&#318;, je zamestn&aacute;vate&#318; na&#271;alej povinn&yacute; odv&aacute;dza&#357; v p&ocirc;vodn&yacute;ch term&iacute;noch splatnosti.<br>
<br>
Zamestn&aacute;vatelia, ktor&yacute;ch zamestnanci vykon&aacute;vaj&uacute; rizikov&uacute; pr&aacute;cu, maj&uacute; tie&#382; n&aacute;rok na odklad povinnosti platenia pr&iacute;spevkov na doplnkov&eacute; d&ocirc;chodkov&eacute; sporenie za t&yacute;chto zamestnancov v rovnakom obdob&iacute;. Rovnako novela umo&#382;&#328;uje odklad platenia pr&iacute;spevkov zamestn&aacute;vate&#318;a na doplnkov&eacute; d&ocirc;chodkov&eacute; sporenie za zamestnanca vykon&aacute;vaj&uacute;ceho pr&aacute;cu zaraden&uacute; na z&aacute;klade rozhodnutia org&aacute;nu &scaron;t&aacute;tnej spr&aacute;vy na &uacute;seku verejn&eacute;ho zdravotn&iacute;ctva do tretej kateg&oacute;rie alebo &scaron;tvrtej kateg&oacute;rie alebo za zamestnanca, ktor&yacute; je tane&#269;n&iacute;kom alebo hudobn&yacute;m umelcom hraj&uacute;cim na dychovom n&aacute;stroji.</div>
</div></div><!-- react-empty: 375 --><!-- react-empty: 376 --><div class="l-main-box border-top border-bottom" data-reactid="377"><div class="articleActions" data-reactid="378"><div class="articleActions-block" data-reactid="379"><iframe src="https://www.facebook.com/plugins/share_button.php?href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.teraz.sk%2Fslovensko%2Fprezidentka-podpisala-moznost-odkladu%2F458364-clanok.html&amp;layout=button_count&amp;size=large&amp;mobile_iframe=false&amp;appId=282867128448169&amp;width=110&amp;height=32" width="110" height="32" style="border:none;overflow:hidden;" scrolling="no" frameborder="0" allowtransparency="true" data-reactid="380"></iframe><a class="socialWidget socialWidget--twitter" href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.teraz.sk%2Fslovensko%2Fprezidentka-podpisala-moznost-odkladu%2F458364-clanok.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-reactid="381"><span class="socialWidget-label" data-reactid="382"><svg class="icon" data-reactid="383"><use xlink:href="/sprite.svg#twitter" data-reactid="384"></use></svg></span></a><a class="socialWidget socialWidget--comments" href="#diskusia" data-reactid="385"><span class="socialWidget-label" data-reactid="386"><svg class="icon" data-reactid="387"><use xlink:href="/sprite.svg#comments" data-reactid="388"></use></svg></span><span class="socialWidget-value" data-reactid="389"><div data-reactid="390"><span class="fb-comments-count" data-href="https://www.teraz.sk/slovensko/prezidentka-podpisala-moznost-odkladu/458364-clanok.html" data-reactid="391">.</span></div></span></a><a class="socialWidget socialWidget" href="mailto:?subject=Teraz.sk%3A%20Prezidentka%20podp%C3%ADsala%20mo%C5%BEnos%C5%A5%20odkladu%20platby%20poistn%C3%BDch%20odvodov&amp;body=Pozri%20si%20tento%20%C4%8Dl%C3%A1nok%20z%20Teraz.sk%3A%0A%0APrezidentka%20podp%C3%ADsala%20mo%C5%BEnos%C5%A5%20odkladu%20platby%20poistn%C3%BDch%20odvodov%0A%20https%3A%2F%2Fwww.teraz.sk%2Fslovensko%2Fprezidentka-podpisala-moznost-odkladu%2F458364-cla